:   Transforms MARC/XML Bibliographic records
:   to RDF conforming to the BIBFRAME model.  Outputs RDF/XML,
:   N-triples, or JSON.
:
:   @author Nate Trail (ntra@loc.gov)
:   @author Kevin Ford (kefo@loc.gov)
:   @since December 17, 2014
:   @version 1.0
:)

(: IMPORTED MODULES :)
